snippet.title: Emily The Strange: Strangerous Nintendo DS
snippet.description: Find the cats, find the one who cat-napped them, and experience the world of Emily the Strange! Emily wakes up after a nightmare in which her cats were cat-napped! Now you must embark on an adventure with Emily to explore the many different worlds that await her. Use a sharp eye to find a way around obstacles and downright Strangerous smarts to solve the many puzzles spread throughout the universe of Emily the Strange! http://www.gamestop.com/ds/games/emily-the-strange-strangerous/91553
